1998;;Desert Blue;;American;;Morgan J. Freeman;;Brendan Sexton III, Kate Hudson, Casey Affleck, Christina Ricci;;comedy drama;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Desert_Blue;;A rising Hollywood starlet (Hudson) becomes "marooned" in a small desert town while on a roadtrip with her father. There, she gets to know the town's rather eccentric residents, including one (Ricci) whose hobby is pipe bombs and another (Sexton) who is trying to carry out his father's dream of building a waterpark in the desert.